---
layout: false
permalink: /about/
---
{%- set totalGroups = 0 %}
{%- for cat in collections.categories %}
  {%- set totalGroups = totalGroups + cat.data.groupCount %}
{%- endfor %}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  {% include "partials/head.njk" %}
  <title>About | {{ site.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Vancouver Community is a free, community-built directory of {{ totalGroups }}+ clubs, meetups, and groups in Vancouver.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="About Vancouver Community">
  <meta property="og:description" content="A free, community-built directory of {{ totalGroups }}+ clubs, meetups, and groups in Vancouver.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url }}/about/">
  <meta property="og:image" content="{{ site.url }}/og-image.png">
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}/about/">
</head>
<body class="category-page">
<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
{% include "partials/topbar.njk" %}
<main id="main-content">
  <div class="cat-hero">
    <div class="prose-hero-wrap">
      <h1 class="cat-title">About Vancouver Community</h1>
      <p class="cat-desc">A free, community-built directory of {{ totalGroups }}+ clubs, meetups, and groups in Vancouver.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-content page-content">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Why this exists</h2>
      <p>Vancouver consistently ranks as one of the hardest cities to make friends. This directory exists to make it a little easier. If you're new to the city, shy, or just looking for your people — start browsing.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Anyone can submit a group via the <a href="/submit/">submit form</a>.</li>
        <li>Submissions are reviewed and added weekly.</li>
        <li>The directory is maintained by <a href="https://bollenbach.ca?ref=vancouvercommunity" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Patrick Bollenbach</a>, a software developer in Vancouver who also built <a href="https://runclubs.ca?ref=vancouvercommunity" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">runclubs.ca</a>.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Press</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>CBC — April 6, 2026</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:vancouver@bolle.co">vancouver@bolle.co</a></p>
      <p>Have a group to add? <a href="/submit/">Submit it here</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="cat-footer page-footer">
    Made by <a href="https://bollenbach.ca?ref=vancouvercommunity" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Patrick Bollenbach</a> in Vancouver. <span id="total-views"></span>
  </div>
</main>
{% include "partials/scripts.njk" %}
</body>
</html>
